jnxLsysSpNATdstruleMIB.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net HTTP://www.juniper.net
jnxLsysSpNATdstruleMIB.description: This module defines the NAT-destination-rule-specific MIB for Juniper Enterprise Logical-System (LSYS) security profiles. Juniper documentation is recommended as the reference. The LSYS security profile provides various static and dynamic resource management by observing resource quota limits. Security NAT-destination-rule resource is the focus in this MIB.
